{"tid":892480,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"孖媽咪外遊 超蓮Pink Lady look潮踎大阪","createTime":"2018-11-07T02:22:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-08T10:02:42.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"cf0a264c27908b7359ebd9e346df14500997bf9b","tid":892480,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T02:22:07.000Z","msg":"近年積極拓展個人事業嘅賭王何鴻燊三房千金何超蓮，除咗顧住盤生意，又會做吓義工行善，亦有踏足時裝同潮流界，可謂百足咁多爪。<br />\n不過，超人都要唞吓氣，所以超蓮終於放假去旅行，佢仲貼相上Instagram同大家開心share，着到一身粉紅色衫嘅佢喺日本街頭大擺甫士影相留念，兼打埋卡透露自己喺大阪。<br />\n今次係同媽咪陳婉珍及朋友同行嘅超蓮，除咗貼出唔少靚相外，亦喺限時動態度post咗好多美食相，除咗有軟綿綿蛋包飯、唔少係蛋類食品外，仲見佢食季節食品添。食咁多好嘢，但超蓮似乎都唔夠，事關佢同行嘅朋友，就貼咗超蓮望住櫥窗中啲甜品模型擘大口得個窿嘅相，睇嚟超蓮下個目標，應該就係甜品喇！<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181106/large/1541503299_b86e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181106%2Flarge%2F1541503299_b86e.jpg&h=a2f940d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181106/large/1541503302_5129.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181106%2Flarge%2F1541503302_5129.jpg&h=a0688f3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181106/large/1541503303_91b7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181106%2Flarge%2F1541503303_91b7.jpg&h=103c973d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20181106/58882396\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181106%2F58882396&d=3tFsguQ86tV6gLW7RkUBT9tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=a5439ba9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181106%2F58882396&h=e2273e46\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledail